FBIS3-32461 "drlat026_o_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-026 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Feb 1994 Colombia * Drug Money Alleged in Congressional Campaigns * Senator Says Allegations `True' 94P20340D Santa Fe de Bogota EL ESPECTADOR in Spanish 10 Jan p 5A 94P20340D Santa Fe de Bogota EL ESPECTADOR Language: Spanish Article Type:CSO [Text] Senator Claudia Blum de Barbieri said during a trip to Leticia that "the report concerning the circulation of drug money to support political campaigns is quite true." She noted however that to control these sources of financing, the Treasury Inspector has been reviewing the candidates' financial books. She said however: "I don't know how well they will be able to cover up the ill-gotten money." She said further that the issue of the so-called hot money is not a new one since that money has been around for some time, especially in Valle Department.
